---

Define

MD5 is another hashing algorithm.

Very popular historically.


---

Why It Was Popular

Fast.

Easy to implement.

Widely supported.


---

Problem

Now considered broken.

Collisions can be generated.


---

Security Reality

Today:

MD5
=
Not suitable
for security


---

Validate

Question:

